Summary: Vehicle #1 was traveling west bound approaching an intersection. Vehicle #2 was traveling east bound traveling through an intersection. V1 attempted to turn south at the intersection and was impacted on the right side by the front bumper of V2. V1 continued south and impacted a utility pole with the front bumper and contacted the left side on a fence.
